	(text "QUESTIONS\n- Should I decouple the board's 5V power line from the analog rail, in order to reduce noise? If so, how?\n- Should I use DAISY chain instead of cascade mode?\n- How should I wire the bias pins? I still don't fully understand how the bias system works.\n- How should I select the resistance and capacitance values in the input RC network?\n- Is the input RC network needed, given that we are already developing the shield module?"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
